 applies runtime system properties for 5.0.1 as well as 5.0.0: `-Dsun.misc.unsafe.memory.access=allow` and `-Dio.netty.tryReflectionSetAccessible=true`. Meaningful tests can use `Vertx.vertx()`, an in-process `HttpServer` bound to `127.0.0.1` on an ephemeral port, and `WebClient`/`CachingWebClient`/`WebClientSession` calls against that server; no external service is required.\",\"risks\":[\"OAuth2-specific Web Client flows depend on optional Vert.x auth modules, but they are not required for meaningful core coverage of requests, responses, forms, redirects, cookies, sessions, and caching.\",\"The local Gradle/native-image run remains authoritative; if Netty changes its Java 25 native requirements, the exact runtime properties may need adjustment.\"]}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_05b62c5a22b7932a016a401d533ae48197aa048f1563b8307d\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1234, "output": 839, "cacheRead": 25600, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 27673, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782586698370, "responseId": "resp_05b62c5a22b7932a016a401d4ad69c8197921d9757fa81557e"}, "toolResults": []}
